Html:
Hi,

You're trying to bind a List to a TextBox. It does not make sense.

To see the difference replace TextBox/Text binding with ListBox/ItemsSource.

This lists the MenuItems in the ListBox.

&lt;tl:Accordion ItemsSource=&quot;{Binding MenuGroups}&quot;&gt;
            &lt;tl:Accordion.ItemTemplate&gt;
                &lt;DataTemplate&gt;
                    &lt;TextBlock Text=&quot;{Binding ModuleName}&quot; /&gt;
                &lt;/DataTemplate&gt;
            &lt;/tl:Accordion.ItemTemplate&gt;
            &lt;tl:Accordion.ContentTemplate&gt;
                &lt;DataTemplate&gt;
                    &lt;ListBox ItemsSource=&quot;{Binding MenuItems}&quot;&gt;
                        &lt;ListBox.ItemTemplate&gt;
                            &lt;DataTemplate&gt;
                                &lt;TextBlock Text=&quot;{Binding MenuItemName}&quot; /&gt;
                            &lt;/DataTemplate&gt;
                        &lt;/ListBox.ItemTemplate&gt;
                    &lt;/ListBox&gt;
                &lt;/DataTemplate&gt;
            &lt;/tl:Accordion.ContentTemplate&gt;
        &lt;/tl:Accordion&gt;

And, Why did you use &quot;/&quot; between MenuItems and MenuItemName?
